sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Index as models-index.yaml<br/>& mcp-servers-index.yaml
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant HF_API as HuggingFace API<br/>huggingface.co<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF_Raw as HuggingFace Raw<br/>huggingface.co/{model}/raw<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>output/ & data/
    participant Konflux as Konflux Build<br/>Tekton Pipeline
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>Container Registry
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>Volume Consumer

    Note over Index,Extractor: Flow 1: Model Metadata Extraction & Catalog Generation

    Index->>Extractor: Read data/models-index.yaml<br/>(File I/O)
    Extractor->>HF_API: GET /api/collections/{org}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (optional)
    HF_API-->>Extractor: Model collections list
    Extractor->>OCI: GET /v2/{image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Public (no auth)
    OCI-->>Extractor: Container manifest + modelcard layer
    Extractor->>HF_Raw: GET /{model}/raw/main/README.md<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (optional)
    HF_Raw-->>Extractor: README with YAML frontmatter
    Extractor->>HF_API: GET /api/models/{model}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (optional)
    HF_API-->>Extractor: Model details (tags, license, downloads)

    Note over Extractor: Multi-source priority resolution:<br/>HF YAML > HF API > Modelcard YAML > Modelcard regex > Generated

    Extractor->>FS: Write output/{model}/enrichment.yaml<br/>(metadata + provenance)
    Extractor->>FS: Write data/models-catalog.yaml<br/>(deduplicated catalog)

    Note over Index,Extractor: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation

    Index->>Extractor: Read data/redhat-mcp-servers-index.yaml<br/>(File I/O)
    Extractor->>OCI: GET /v2/{mcp-image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Public
    OCI-->>Extractor: MCP server image manifest<br/>(architectures, timestamps)
    Extractor->>FS: Write input/mcp_servers/*/enrichment<br/>(in-place writeback)
    Extractor->>FS: Write data/redhat-mcp-servers-catalog.yaml

    Note over FS,Dashboard: Flow 3: Container Image Build & Deployment

    FS->>Konflux: COPY data/*.yaml /app/data/<br/>(Dockerfile.konflux)
    Konflux->>Quay: Push odh-model-metadata-collection<br/>HTTPS/443 | Registry credentials
    Note over Dashboard: Data container runs:<br/>CMD ["sleep", "infinity"]
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Mount data container volume<br/>Read /app/data/*.yaml catalogs
